          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Choose an animal companion: dog, wolf, mountain lion, panther, or an equivalent animal approved by your game master. Your pet has stats equal to a minion creature profile of your character level except that it always acts on initiative 1. If your pet ever dies, you may spend 1 week of dedicated in-game time acquiring a new pet of your choice from the below list. You and the game master can use this time to roleplay how you come about acquiring a new pet.",
